*ipw2200-0.15 (25 Nov 2004)

  25 Nov 2004; Jeremy Maitin-Shepard <jbms@gentoo.org> +ipw2200-0.15.ebuild,
  -ipw2200-0.3.ebuild, -ipw2200-0.4-r1.ebuild, -ipw2200-0.4.ebuild,
